---
title: Roasted Vegetable Quesadillas with Chipotle-Chili Mayo and Guacamole
description: In our book, quesadillas and guacamole are the ultimate comfort food. Stuffed with lightly caramelized asparagus and bell pepper, these quesadillas are indulgent yet wholesome. A secret layer of chipotle mayo will forever change the way you make quesadillas.
